Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Spring heatwave, 1976
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z99kv
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 25 Apr 1976
Spring heatwave. Congress wants more say on foreign policy. White exodus from New York. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less